description: The outskirts of Prague are always a good spot for hunting adorable young men. Often they themselves have no idea how adorable they are. And it is up to us "hunters" to show them their high value. Today I was a bit lazy and I just waited at a less frequented walkway until I saw an attractive boy passing by. I approached him and offered him some money for showing me his chest. Obviously he didn´t trust me in the first moment. But I still persuaded him for a hot striptease in front of all the joggers and walkers around. He noticed very soon what I am interested in. He assured me that he never did something similar before. And I was all too curious to find out how far he would go. Don´t miss this cutie.
title: Czech Hunter 62
